<p>Alleged imposition of the death penalty on an individual with reported psychosocial 
</p>
<p>disabilities. According to the information received, Mr. Warren Hill was sentenced to 
</p>
<p>death in August 1991 for the murder of a prison inmate in August 1990. According to 
</p>
<p>the new information received, on 20 January 2015, the Supreme Court of Georgia in a 
</p>
<p>5-2 ruling denied Mr. Hill&#8217;s application for probable cause to appeal the denial of 
</p>
<p>habeas corpus. His execution is scheduled to take place on 27 January 2015. A press 
</p>
