<p>or on charges of &#8220;illegal business activity&#8221; and &#8220;inciting subversion&#8221;. Some of them 
</p>
<p>are allegedly detained at Beijing No.1 Detention Centre, whilst the whereabouts of the 
</p>
<p>other individuals are unknown. Reportedly, none of them has been permitted access to 
</p>
<p>a lawyer.  
</p>
<p>30/03/2015 
