<p> <b> B. Replies received between 1 February and 30 April 2015 relating to communications sent before 1 
</b></p>
<p><b>December 2014 
</b></p>
<p>11. The table below lists, in chronological order, communications dating before 1 December 2014 to which a reply or an 
</p>
<p>additional reply has been received in the period between 1 February and 30 April 2015. Copies of the full text of the 
</p>
<p>communications sent and the reply received during the reporting period can be accessed from the electronic version of this report 
</p>
<p>available on the OHCHR website. Some names of individuals or other information have been rendered anonymous or otherwise 
</p>
<p>unidentifiable. Government replies to cases COL 6/2014, HUN 2/2013, IRQ 5/2014, SAU 2/2014, SAU 12/2014, THA 4/2014, 
</p>
<p>TUN 2/2014, and VEN 7/2014 were omitted in the previous reports A/HRC/24/21 and A/HRC/28/85 due to technical problems and 
</p>
