<p><b>Summary 
</b></p>
<p><b>executions;   
</b></p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>Allegations of summary executions of nine persons in the South-East region of Ukraine. 
</p>
<p>According to the information received, on 23 September 2014, two unmarked graves 
</p>
<p>were discovered near the Kommunar coal mine, 60 km from Donetsk, which until a few 
</p>
<p>days before the discovery had been controlled by the Ukrainian National Guard 
</p>
<p>battalion. A total of nine bodies were exhumed, including those of three women. 
</p>
<p>Concerns are expressed about the discovery of the graves and that the nine persons 
</p>
<p>appear to have been summarily executed. 
</p>
<p>08/04/2015 
</p>
