<p> 
</p>
<p>Letter concerning discriminatory provisions against women in nationality legislation. 
</p>
<p>According to the information received, current nationality law in Kuwait discriminates 
</p>
<p>against women in that fathers can confer their nationality to their children in all 
</p>
<p>circumstances while mothers cannot. 
