<p><b>Discrimination 
</b></p>
<p><b>against women ;   
</b></p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>Letter concerning discriminatory provisions against women in nationality legislation. 
</p>
<p>According to the information received, current nationality law in Qatar discriminates 
</p>
<p>against women in that they are not permitted to transfer their nationality to their 
</p>
<p>children under any circumstances even if this would result in statelessness. 
